My face because I *actually* showered makeupped and left the house today.
I am marrying my baby daddy 🫶🏻 I love you, honey. I love our family. You’ve made me so happy 💙
happy birthday to my best buddy 🫧🫶🏻🩵
Get ya broke selves on my level 🥂

I hate the word dump, so here are my Fourth of July pleasantries. Take care to notice my dog exploring a box of old fireworks and my Brazilian fiancé in his american T-shirt. The most atrocious early 2000’s country was the soundtrack of the holiday. We tried to go to Joshua tree but the airbnb was actually in Palmdale “in Joshua TreeS” 😩😂🩵🌹🤍

Had the absolute pleasure of making a house call to Joshua Tree for @lindsleyregister bachelorette party🙇🏻‍♀️🫶🏻!!

I’ve been talking with my clients lately about how magical the energy has felt with each one of you that I’ve been honored to poke! I’m so lucky to attract such incredible people to my table.

Miss bride and I talked about things she wanted on her personalized flash sheet for her special day and we came up with a super sweet sheet just for them!! I always bring my flash book with me as well, as permanency is a big deal! 🫶🏻

Had the coolest assist ⭐️( @frog.pokes )⭐️

Each one of these sweetie girls’ first handpoke and one baby’s FIRST TATTOO ❤️!

To say the least, my heart is FULL and I’m so happy to have been a part of celebrating this sweetheart !

As always, dm for booking !

(house call or koreatown) 

LOVE YOU
Happy birthday to you, my love🩵
never take a palm tree for granted
Summer isn’t over. My highlights say so.
Like a fine wine baby. Thank you all for making my birthday so special. 🍐
You are okay. We are okay. 🫶🏻
